{"tid":2111453,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"警方將以搜查令搜查理大","createTime":"2020-07-16T14:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T15:41:20.000Z","uid":325023,"like":9,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"0853c351177312e6de4cf228b78b6b22094b64ad","tid":2111453,"uid":325023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:09:09.000Z","msg":"【警方將以搜查令搜查理大】<br />\n<br />\n香港理工大學學生會收到通知，警方將於明天（ 2020年7月17日）早上時段，手持搜查令，搜查香港理工大學校園範圍。警方聲稱該手令是用以調查一宗暴動罪，據知與當日理大事件中發生的事情有關。<br />\n<br />\n學生會將會全力跟進此事，請各界關注的友好朋友關注並廣傳之，我們會定時向公眾報告事態發展。<br />\n<br />\nsource: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/395371830546153/posts/3101850883231554/?sfnsn=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F395371830546153%2Fposts%2F3101850883231554%2F%3Fsfnsn%3Dmo&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFabZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=8fbdb5cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/395371830546153/posts/3101850883231554/?sfnsn=mo</a>"},{"pid":"e1c3f65e3dab9919ab37d431944a2fd4eca53552","tid":2111453,"uid":231583,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:10:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"744a75131e531c074365348a696cab5798f8d253","tid":2111453,"uid":106604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:22:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1f04275bb77897a0bc6aeb0277b9e98bd02185a","tid":2111453,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:22:23.000Z","msg":"成大半年先查？無野下話？"},{"pid":"5bc3b07bcfe582ce2e7af48e8e22b0cf33fa963a","tid":2111453,"uid":50972,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:23:26.000Z","msg":"大半年後 裝修哂先去？"},{"pid":"241a919e171d292f5111359cba40a9fefc9fd5e5","tid":2111453,"uid":45910,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T14:23:31.000Z","msg":"得閒返支那抗洪啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/no